title: 'Jurassic World: Dominion' Is EVERYTHING Wrong with Hollywood
description:
"Jurassic World" debuted this weekend, and wow, did it suck! We tell you how hard. Also, AOC is starting to stab Joe Biden in the back. We should keep an eye on that one. And who has a crappier job: assistant coach of the Washington Commanders or the guy who collects Putin's poop? #JurassicWorld #January6 #PatriotFront
